'''''Tsotsi''''' ni  film yanditswe na tuyoborwa Gavin Hood na  Petero Fudakowski muri 2005 nibwo yasohotse<ref>Tsotsi - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › tsotsi</ref>. ''Ni uguhuza'' igitabo cyitwa Tsotsi, cyanditswe na Athol Fugard Afurika yepfo / Ubwongereza bukorana<ref>Tsotsi | Development Education Review <nowiki>https://www.developmenteducationreview.com</nowiki> › issue-5</ref>.  [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]], hagaragaramo Presley Chweneyagae nka David / Tsotsi ( ''izina rya Tsotsitaal'' ryitwa "inkozi y'ibibi"), umusore wibye  imodoka gusa abona umwana yicaye inyuma<ref>Tsotsi | The Guardian <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › culture › mar</ref>. Irimo kandi Terry Pheto, Kenneth Nkosi, Jerry Mofokeng, na Rapulana Seiphemo<ref>Tsotsi won't be bringing home the loot - The Mail & Guardian <nowiki>https://mg.co.za</nowiki> › Article</ref> . 

Amajwi y'iyi filime agaragaza umuziki wa Kwaito wakozwe n'umuhanzi wo muri Afurika y'Epfo Zola ndetse n'amanota ya Mark Kilian na Paul Hepker agaragaza ijwi ry'umuririmbyi wo muri Afurika y'Epfo wigaragambyaga akaba n'umusizi Vusi Mahlasela<ref>Tsotsi Cast and Crew - Cast Photos and Info | Fandango <nowiki>https://www.fandango.com</nowiki> › tsotsi-94478 › cast-and-cr...</ref> .

Iyi filime yakunzwe cyane, ishimwa cyane cyane iyandikwa, icyerekezo, ndetse n’imikorere<ref>Tsotsi Movie Synopsis, Summary, Plot & Film Details <nowiki>https://www.filmjabber.com</nowiki> › movie-synopsis › tsotsi</ref>, cyane cyane ibya Chweneyagae na Pheto, sinema n’uburemere bw’amarangamutima<ref>Tsotsi knowledge organiser - Oasis Academy Oldham <nowiki>https://www.oasisacademyoldham.org</nowiki> › Curriculum</ref>. Yakomeje gutsindira igihembo cya Akademiki cya 2006 muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga kandi itorwa muri Golden Globe muri Filime Nziza y’indimi z’amahanga<ref>Tsotsi: from Fugard to film - De Gruyter <nowiki>https://www.degruyter.com</nowiki> › entry › iab20122602 › html</ref>, iba filime ya mbere yo muri Afurika yepfo ndetse na filime ya mbere nyafurika idakozwe mu [[Igifaransa|gifaransa]] yatsindinze.    Muri 2009, yasubiwemo kumugaragaro muri [[Igitamili|Tamil]] nka ''Yogi'' <ref>Yogi is the remake of Tsotsi - FilmiBeat <nowiki>https://www.filmibeat.com</nowiki> › tamil › news</ref>.<ref>Ameer confused about releasing 'Yogi' - The New Indian ... <nowiki>https://www.newindianexpress.com</nowiki> › tamil › nov › ame...</ref>
